title: 2017 Thailand Champions Cup
text:
The 2017 Thailand Champions Cup was the first <a href="Thailand%20Champions%20Cup">Thailand Champions Cup</a>, an annual <a href="association%20football">football</a> match contested by the winners of the previous season's <a href="Thai%20League%201">Thai League 1</a> and <a href="Thai%20FA%20Cup">Thai FA Cup</a> competitions. The match was played at <a href="National%20Stadium%20%28Thailand%29">Supachalasai Stadium</a>, <a href="Bangkok">Bangkok</a> and contested by <a href="2016%20Thai%20League%20T1">2016 Thai League T1</a> champions <a href="Muangthong%20United%20F.C.">SCG Muangthong United</a>, and <a href="Sukhothai%20F.C.">Sukhothai</a> as the champions of the <a href="2016%20Thai%20FA%20Cup">2016 Thai FA Cup</a>.
Match.
